Package: omnibench.logger
Type: Package
Title: Streaming Structured Logger for Omnibenchmark Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("btraven", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "ben.uzh@proton.me")
Description: Lightweight JSONL event logger for Snakemake-driven
    omnibenchmark pipelines. Provides init_logger() and emit() to
    record start/end events conforming to the omnibench-events 0.1
    wire spec.
